data.description: Beautiful home in a quiet swim/tennis community. Cul-de-sac lot with a private flat backyard. Modern kitchen with granite countertops that overlooks into family room. The master bath has a large dual vanity that includes a vanity area, a generous-sized soaking tub and a separate shower. The over-sized basement is finished with a complete bathroom & bedroom. Must see!!!!
